\n係反就反，失敗主義撚陰啲陰啲<br />\n又扮下支持港獨又扮下黃絲噉</blockquote><br />\n有兩班五毛合作架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一班明做 好似JR D_Wade 三色貓呢班 一班就陰d陰d暗做 兩班合作 暗做個班無咁易俾人察覺呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/175935_3f3cb9a995a485b61cf145308737e32a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F175935_3f3cb9a995a485b61cf145308737e32a.jpg&h=9601e6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陰啲陰啲吹奏支那人高質過香港人<br />\n賤種五毛</blockquote><br />\n五毛狗毛澤東真係好撚陰險,我個次只係針對討論曼德拉效應呢個單一事件對兩個論壇既評價，五毛狗毛澤東就想混淆其他人將我係評價成個lihkg"},{"pid":"c2bb3b77e9bc55875af84d5c9871afa13391931a","tid":420974,"uid":28309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:00:55.000Z","msg":"五毛開始轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個著眼點根本係公投上面"},{"pid":"e4f2a2b32035c286a7437600f8481f7e76b6f9a1","tid":420974,"uid":3117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五毛開始轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個著眼點根本係公投上面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班五毛一直係度香港點樣失敗點樣唔掂，又話有公投都唔掂，記得之前有個電話訪問已經有4成幾人贊成獨立，班五毛就講到香港人9成唔會揀獨立，知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2c44015c9021fc7fa324d5172ee8b62f0e8393","tid":420974,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>證明五毛真心驚任何獨立意識</strong></span>"},{"pid":"510d1be5c6fb5f50d036f56fcbb255a01739643d","tid":420974,"uid":91721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>證明五毛真心驚任何獨立意識</strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獨立意識就算短期無辦法推動公投/建國，都會為中間派帶嚟好籌碼以增加自治權(如推動普選)<br />\n<br />\n所以獨立意識對香港人只有好處"},{"pid":"b144e8a4324a8866dae93b684157a1f545cf74be","tid":420974,"uid":76261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>證明五毛真心驚任何獨立意識</strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獨立意識就算短期無辦法推動公投/建國，都會為中間派帶嚟好籌碼以增加自治權(如推動普選)<br />\n<br />\n所以獨立意識對香港人只有好處</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意"},{"pid":"915b6c0b7eddbbbd73bdcef23bc33248c9998b06","tid":420974,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>證明五毛真心驚任何獨立意識</strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獨立意識就算短期無辦法推動公投/建國，都會為中間派帶嚟好籌碼以增加自治權(如推動普選)<br />\n<br />\n所以獨立意識對香港人只有好處</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意</blockquote><br />\n開天殺價落地還錢嘅理論<br />\n雨革時講過，依家啲人扮失憶<br />\n香港人思維偏向商業、講溝通、協商<br />\n同保守派係間空氣有限嘅房到，你話不如開窗，啲保守派會話不動最好<br />\n但如果你係話要拆咗個天花板，啲保守派後而會容許你開窗<br />\n再講香港一定要有民族主義，依個係冇討論空間，除非你係移民，每個香港人心底都係有民族認同感，但表現出嚟嘅係另一句事，好多時只係為求個眾人皆醉我獨醒嘅快感"},{"pid":"e6cdf336286abf696a203b35a833961794cef95b","tid":420974,"uid":1248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T21:21:26.000Z","msg":"只會用人地既成功黎屌鳩自己人<br />\n人地長時間既努力就唔識拎去借鏡"},{"pid":"eb2d48f4853d264536cf316fb1249cfb7e6df1cb","tid":420974,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T23:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df793465f01f11b3ff7f43109ce0e36f9bfcab2","tid":420974,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T23:28:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9021642a1c1a36f826e94acf6b3e4a0843fa0d18","tid":420974,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T23:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eed91487d46ce7f87740024c285aaabc693ff56","tid":420974,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk